BASED ON ACTUAL EVENTS.

00:08.217 --> 00:11.011
CHARACTERS AND EVENTS WERE
ADAPTED FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT

00:12.012 --> 00:14.348
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

00:16.000 --> 00:22.074
